  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Harry</b> is a name and a nickname in Westeros.\n</p><p>Characters named <b>Harry</b> include:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Harry_Merrell\" title=\"Harry Merrell\">Harry Merrell</a>, one of Jaime Lannister's men</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Harry_Rivers\" title=\"Harry Rivers\">Harry Rivers</a>, the bastard of Jonos Bracken</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Harry_Sawyer\" title=\"Harry Sawyer\">Harry Sawyer</a>, a supporter of Renly Baratheon</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Harry_Strickland\" title=\"Harry Strickland\">Harry Strickland</a>, the captain-general in command of the Golden Company</li></ul>\n<p>Characters nicknamed <b>Harry</b> include:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Harrold_Hardyng\" title=\"Harrold Hardyng\">Harrold Hardyng</a>, the heir of Robert Arryn</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Harrion_Karstark\" title=\"Harrion Karstark\">Harrion Karstark</a>, son of Rickard Karstark</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404220002\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.004 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.004 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 4/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 1/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:20776-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404220002 and revision id 163749\n -->\n",
